description:
As a user
  I want to add products from different categories to my cart
  So that I can purchase items from various product categories

elements.name: Add one product from each category to cart

steps.name: I am logged in to the application
I select the "Electronics" category
I add "Wireless Headphones" to the cart
I select the "Clothing" category
I add "Classic T-Shirt" to the cart
I select the "Books" category
I add "The Great Gatsby" to the cart
I select the "Home & Kitchen" category
I add "Coffee Maker" to the cart
I navigate to the cart page
I should see 4 items in my cart
I should see "Wireless Headphones" in my cart
I should see "Classic T-Shirt" in my cart
I should see "The Great Gatsby" in my cart
I should see "Coffee Maker" in my cart

name: Add Products to Cart

description:
As a user
  I want to login to the application
  So that I can access my account and shop for products

steps.name: I navigate to the login page
I enter username "spider" and password "Spider@1234"
I click the submit button
I should be logged in successfully
I should be redirected to the home page

name: User Login
